# Subject, about 50 characters
# <type>[optional scope]: <imperative description>
#
# types: fix, feat, chore, docs, style, test, refactor, perf, revert
# scopes: api, routing, scss, tos, orders, riven, agents, etc.
#
# Use present tense: "fix order validation", not "fixed order validation".

# Body, wrap at 72 characters
# Explain the problem and solution when the subject is not enough.
# Include verification, for example:
# Tested: yarn test
# Not run: yarn build (reason)

# Footer, wrap at 72 characters
# Refs #123
# Fixes #123